# Transformer Auto-Calculation Suite (for Mahati Industries)

> **Note:** This is a custom-built web application **specially made for Mahati Industries** to support its engineering and design teams.

## ðŸš€ Overview

This project is a comprehensive suite of web-based calculators that consolidate numerous complex transformer design and analysis calculations into a single, easy-to-use interface. It is designed to automate, standardize, and accelerate the technical design process specifically for Mahati Industries.

### How to Run This Project
To access all the calculation tools, simply open the **`Main page.html`** file in your web browser. This Main Page acts as the central hub and provides links to all the individual calculation modules.

---

## ðŸ§® Calculations Included

This suite provides dedicated modules for the following critical transformer calculations:

* Current Density Calculation
* Eddy and Stray Loss Calculation
* Losses & Copper Weight Calculation
* No Load Current Calculation
* No Load Losses
* Cooling Calculation
* Core Hotspot Temp Calculation
* Hotspot Temp Rise Calculation
* Impedance Calculation
* Inrush Current Calculation
* PRV Calculation
* Regulation Calculation
* Short Circuit Calculation Thermal (Normal tap)
* Short Circuit Calculation Dynamic (at normal tap)
* Short Circuit Calculation Dynamic (at negative tap)
* Short Circuit Calculator (Thermal)

## ðŸ’» Technology

This is a lightweight, frontend-only tool built with:

* **HTML5:** For the structure of the calculator pages.
* **CSS3:** For styling and user interface.
* **JavaScript:** For all the core engineering calculation logic.
